nt trembling seized them, he prayed: \"O my Sustainer! Hadst Thou so willed, Thou wouldst have destroyed them ere this, and me [with them]. Wilt Thou destroy us for what the weak-minded among us have done? (All] this is but a trial from Thee, whereby Thou allowest to go astray whom Thou willest, and guidest aright whom Thou willest. Thou art near unto us: grant us, then, forgiveness and have mercy on us - for Thou art the best of all forgivers!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1109.mp3","surahId":7,"words":[{"id":81129,"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱخْتَارَ","translation":"এবং বেছে নিলো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_155_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81130,"position":2,"arabic":"مُوسَىٰ","translation":"মূসা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_155_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81131,"position":3,"arabic":"قَوْمَهُۥ","translation":"তার জাতির","audioUrl":"wbw/007_155_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81132,"position":4,"arabic":"سَبْعِينَ","translation":"সত্তর (জন)","audioUrl":"wbw/007_155_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81133,"position":5,"arabic":"رَجُلًۭا","translation":"লোককে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_155_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81134,"position":6,"arabic":"لِّمِيقَـٰتِنَا ۖ","translation":"জন্যে আমাদের নির্ধারিত স্থানের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_155_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81136,"position":7,"arabic":"فَلَمَّآ","translation":"অতঃপর যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/007_155_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81137,"position":8,"arabic":"أَخَذَتْهُمُ","translation":"ধরলো তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_155_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81138,"position":9,"arabic":"ٱلرَّجْفَةُ","translation":"ভূমিকম্প","audioUrl":"wbw/007_155_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81139,"position":10,"arabic":"قَالَ","translation":"সে বললো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_155_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81140,"position":11,"arabic":"رَبِّ","translation":"\"হে আমার রব","audioUrl":"wbw/007_155_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81141,"position":1